{"tid":992360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美眾院通過法案　支持台灣重獲世衛觀察員身分","createTime":"2019-01-23T06:11:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T00:08:48.000Z","uid":141151,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"84b4916fd50cdd86e5517a418f3841d69287fcef","tid":992360,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T06:11:45.000Z","msg":"美眾院通過法案　支持台灣重獲世衛觀察員身分<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20190123/s00005/1548204845182/%E7%BE%8E%E7%9C%BE%E9%99%A2%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88-%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E9%87%8D%E7%8D%B2%E4%B8%96%E8%A1%9B%E8%A7%80%E5%AF%9F%E5%93%A1%E8%BA%AB%E5%88%86\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20190123%2Fs00005%2F1548204845182%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E7%259C%25BE%25E9%2599%25A2%25E9%2580%259A%25E9%2581%258E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%258D%25B2%25E4%25B8%2596%25E8%25A1%259B%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%25AF%259F%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E5%2588%2586&d=tutJX9Q1VHv%2FYSiL6Mt37b%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=ff39ae07\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20190123%2Fs00005%2F1548204845182%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E7%259C%25BE%25E9%2599%25A2%25E9%2580%259A%25E9%2581%258E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%258D%25B2%25E4%25B8%2596%25E8%25A1%259B%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%25AF%259F%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E5%2588%2586&h=0823fc11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20190123/s00005/1548204845182/%E7%BE%8E%E7%9C%BE%E9%99%A2%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88-%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E9%87%8D%E7%8D%B2%E4%B8%96%E8%A1%9B%E8%A7%80%E5%AF%9F%E5%93%A1%E8%BA%AB%E5%88%86</a><br />\n<br />\n世界衛生大會（WHA）去年5月在瑞士日內瓦召開，台灣連續第二年未獲邀請出席。<span style=\"color: red;\">美國眾議院周二（22日）<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無異議</span>下，通過支持台灣重返世衛（WHO）的法案，法案將交予參議院表決。</span><br />\n<br />\n法案指出，台灣自2009年起以觀察員身分參加世界衛生大會，但在總統蔡英文於2016年上台後，台灣國際空間遭大陸打壓，同年世衛大會遲遲未向台灣發邀請，2017和2018年更是未有獲邀。法案要求美國國務卿蓬佩奧，研究讓台灣重獲世衛觀察員身分的策略。<br />\n<br />\n今次法案原已於去年的美國眾議院表決通過，但因參議院議程繁多而未能表決；按照規定，新國會在本月3日召開後，所有未經參眾兩院通過的法案，皆須重新提案。<span style=\"color: red;\">重提的法案繼續獲共和黨及民主黨支持。</span><br />\n<br />\n（中央社）"},{"pid":"9d52372c896809d7a8bcbd80cda0421336360af5","tid":992360,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T06:24:56.000Z","msg":"過到先算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adb81208e70c358761e910b1ce98fb26fc612d90","tid":992360,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d52372c896809d7a8bcbd80cda0421336360af5","tid":992360,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T06:24:56.000Z","msg":"過到先算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T06:37:53.000Z","msg":"中國實叫埋班非洲契弟一齊反對, 實過唔到"},{"pid":"ef961a6f1a6402caa1612232ffa3d0ca9796731b","tid":992360,"uid":30633,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T13:44:31.000Z","msg":"讓世人見到中國有幾仆街<br />\n有豬瘟都唔同台灣通報"},{"pid":"5ee5ee6bab1c86ad5cb24260a0f53ce617ad8afb","tid":992360,"uid":54824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T13:57:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>無異議下</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db0b9c2924dcfd80ff929f5be547a6ef09f0e8ac","tid":992360,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T18:53:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e00959e29f9614fe75d398a062a34315f8f9bbb","tid":992360,"uid":75326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedB